title: NURS 333 Professional Nursing Practice with Childbearing Women, Infants, and their Families
description: Analysis and application of theories, concepts, evidence and competencies guiding professional nursing practice with childbearing women and families during the transition to parenthood in a variety of practice settings and contexts.
prerequisites: All of NURS 302, NURS 303, NURS 304, NURS 305, NURS 306.
